metadata.name: I'm Slowly Fading Away
metadata.description:
In a dystopian city ridden by urban decay, overpopulation and economic blight, how relevant is human emotion?  This collection takes a cinematic approach to put into contrast the vulnerability of our emotions against a dark reality in the form of movie subtitles.  

Shot on Leica M6 with Fujifilm Industrial 100 Film
Hong Kong, 2021
3000 x 1989
